cu.explanation_en: Setting the NG AMF IP address to an invalid IP format will cause configuration parsing failure.

du.explanation_en: Setting the downlink frequency band to 1000 exceeds the maximum allowed value, causing configuration validation error.
du.explanation_zh: 將下行頻率帶設定為 1000 超過最大允許值，會導致配置驗證錯誤。
